'''Gabrielle''' (born 1962) and '''Gretchen Hawskon''' (1962 - 1997), collectively known as the '''Hawkson Twins''', were an American duo of twin sisters. Their father was soldier-turned-spy [[Eagle Hawkson]]. Gabrielle is the surviving twin following Gretchen's death in 1997 from a car accident. 

